'''瑞秋·诺特利'''（{{lang|en|Rachel Notley}}，{{bd|1964年|4月17日|catIdx=Notley}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]][[政治人物|政治人物]]，2015-19年間任職第17任[[阿尔伯塔省省長|阿尔伯塔省省長]]。她為現任亞省新民主黨[[黨魁|黨魁]]及[[亞伯達省議會|亞伯達省議會]]愛民頓-士達孔拿選區省議員。她於2008年首度晉身省議會，再於2014年當選新民主黨黨魁和2015年宣誓就任[[省長_(加拿大)|省長]]，成為該省首位新民主黨黨籍省長。新民主黨於2019年省選敗予[[聯合保守黨|聯合保守黨]]成為省議會第二大黨，諾特利遂改任亞省官方反對黨主席。

==生平==
===背景===
瑞秋·諾特利於1964年在[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]][[愛民頓|愛民頓]]出生<ref>{{cite news |title=Riding profile: Mill Woods, Strathcona and Meadowlark |url=http://www2.canada.com/edmontonjournal/features/albertavotes/story.html?id=dff895ae-39b1-401d-a339-29d957e5058d |work=Edmonton Journal |publisher=Canada.com |date=February 24, 2008 |accessdate=May 4, 2012 |archive-date=2015-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525035136/http://www2.canada.com/edmontonjournal/features/albertavotes/story.html?id=dff895ae-39b1-401d-a339-29d957e5058d |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後在該省西北部的[[费尔维尤市|費爾維尤]]長大。父親格蘭特（{{lang|en|Grant Notley}}）於1968年成為亞省新民主黨[[黨魁|黨魁]]，再於1971年當選[[亞伯達省議會|亞伯達省議會]]斯比里特河-費爾維尤選區（{{lang|en|Spirit River-Fairview}}）省議員<ref name=legislative>[https://www.assembly.ab.ca/net/index.aspx?p=mla_bio&rnumber=41 Legislative Assembly of Alberta]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901105114/https://www.assembly.ab.ca/net/index.aspx?p=mla_bio&rnumber=41 |date=2011-09-01 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hermis.alberta.ca/PAA/Details.aspx?st=%22Legislative+Assembly%22&cp=20&sort=department&ReturnUrl=%2FPAA%2FSearch.aspx%3Fst%3D%2522Legislative%2BAssembly%2522%26cp%3D20%26sort%3Ddepartment&dv=True&DeptID=1&ObjectID=PR1560 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-10-20 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020132733/https://hermis.alberta.ca/PAA/Details.aspx?st=%22Legislative+Assembly%22&cp=20&sort=department&ReturnUrl=%2FPAA%2FSearch.aspx%3Fst%3D%22Legislative+Assembly%22&cp=20&sort=department&dv=True&DeptID=1&ObjectID=PR1560 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1984年10月19日遇上空難逝世<ref name=notleypoliticalstar>{{cite web|last1=Cosh|first1=Colby|title=How Rachel Notley became Canada's most surprising political star|url=http://www.macleans.ca/politics/how-rachel-notley-became-canadas-most-surprising-political-star/|work=《[[麥克林|麥克林]]》雜誌|date=May 21, 2015|accessdate=May 22, 2015|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811162838/https://www.macleans.ca/politics/how-rachel-notley-became-canadas-most-surprising-political-star/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

諾特利於1987年從[[亞伯達大學|亞伯達大學]]獲取政治學學士學位<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ualberta.ca/newtrail/autumn-2016/bear-country/wildfire-heroes |title=Alumni Among Wildfire Heroes |publisher=[[亞伯達大學|亞伯達大學]] |accessdate=2016-10-20 |date=2016-08-05 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327070826/https://www.ualberta.ca/newtrail/autumn-2016/bear-country/wildfire-heroes |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後到[[約克大學_(加拿大)|約克大學]]奧斯古法學院（{{lang|en|Osgoode Hall Law School}}）攻讀法律，1990年畢業<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.osgoode.yorku.ca/news/congratulations-to-osgoode-alum-and-alberta-premier-elect-rachel-notley-90-on-her-election-victory/ |title=Congratulations to Osgoode alum and Alberta Premier-elect Rachel Notley '90 on her election victory |publisher=奧斯古法學院 |accessdate=2016-10-20 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608093402/https://www.osgoode.yorku.ca/news/congratulations-to-osgoode-alum-and-alberta-premier-elect-rachel-notley-90-on-her-election-victory/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=about>{{cite web |url=http://www.ndpopposition.ab.ca/rachelnotley/node/4 |title=About Rachel - Alberta NDP |publisher=Alberta NDP Opposition |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706164108/http://www.ndpopposition.ab.ca/rachelnotley/node/4 |archivedate=July 6, 2011}}</ref>後為愛民頓勞工律師布雷克利（{{lang|en|Bob Blakely}}）實習，其後入職亞伯達省政府僱員工會，為因工受傷的工會會員爭取權益。

諾特利於1994年遷至[[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[溫哥華|溫哥華]]，成為卑詩健康科學協會的職業健康及安全代表<ref>The Report: Newsletter of the Health Sciences Association of BC ''[http://www.hsabc.org/viewReport.php?rid=32&page=2&id=99&sid=7] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hsabc.org/viewReport.php?rid=32&page=2&id=99&sid=7 |date=20121212172823 }} Safety concerns in your workplace? See your Safety Steward!''</ref>，並曾任卑詩省律政廳長[[杜新志|杜新志]]的助理<ref name=notleypoliticalstar/>。她於2002年返回愛民頓，先後在全國公共及普通僱員工會<ref>NUPGE website ''{{cite web |url=http://www.nupge.ca/news_2002/news_oc02/n14oc02b.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20060529172937/http://www.nupge.ca/news_2002/news_oc02/n14oc02b.htm |archivedate=2006-05-29 }}  Nationwide campaign targets Liberal inaction on medicare''</ref>、阿薩巴斯卡大學<ref>Athabasca University 2004/05 Calendar''{{cite web |url=http://www.athabascau.ca/calendar/page10_10_03.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060210041815/http://www.athabascau.ca/calendar/page10_10_03.html |archivedate=2006-02-10 }}''</ref>和亞伯達護士工會等機構工作<ref name=about/>。

諾特利的丈夫魯·阿拉布（{{lang|en|Lou Arab}}）為加拿大公共僱員工會的通訊代表<ref name=2007biography/>，兩人育有兩名子女，一家居於愛民頓的老士達孔拿社區（{{lang|en|Old Strathcona}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/rachel-notley-is-the-new-leader-of-the-alberta-ndp-1.2804396 |title=Rachel mania: what makes NDP's Notley the 'right leader?' |date=May 9, 2015 |first=Marion |last=Warnica |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=May 17, 2015 |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223054316/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/rachel-notley-is-the-new-leader-of-the-alberta-ndp-1.2804396 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ABAssembly">{{cite web |url=https://www.assembly.ab.ca/net/index.aspx?p=mla_bio&rnumber=45&leg=29 |title=Premier Rachel Notley (ND) |publisher=[[亞伯達省議會|亞伯達省議會]] |accessdate=2016-10-20 |date=2015-11-25 |archive-date=2018-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212181743/http://www.assembly.ab.ca/net/index.aspx?p=mla_bio&rnumber=45&leg=29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===晉身省政===
[[File:Alberta_Budget_2009_NDP_MLA_Rachel_Notley.jpg|thumb]]

諾特利於1991年加入亞省新民主黨的競選策劃委員會，為1993年省選準備；新民主黨在該屆省選並未贏得任何議席<ref name=notleypoliticalstar/>。隨著巴勒特（{{lang|en|Pam Barrett}}）於2000年辭去亞省新民主黨黨魁和愛民頓-高地選區省議員職務，當時仍居於卑詩省的諾特利返回愛民頓，參與新民主黨候選人美臣（{{lang|en|Brian Mason}}）角逐該選區議席的競選工作<ref name=notleypoliticalstar/>。

她曾考慮參與2004年省選，但因她兩名子女當時仍年幼而放棄<ref name=activismprotest>{{cite web|last1=Bennett|first1=Dean|title=Alberta NDP Leader Rachel Notley started activism in childhood protest marches|url=http://edmonton.ctvnews.ca/alberta-ndp-leader-rachel-notley-started-activism-in-childhood-protest-marches-1.2060445|publisher=CTV News|accessdate=17 May 2015|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414195114/https://edmonton.ctvnews.ca/alberta-ndp-leader-rachel-notley-started-activism-in-childhood-protest-marches-1.2060445|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年10月，她在無對手競爭的情況下贏取亞省新民主黨候選人提名，在來屆省選代表該黨角逐[[亞伯達省議會|亞伯達省議會]]愛民頓-士達孔拿選區議席<ref name=2007biography/>。她於2008年省選贏取該議席，首度晉身省議會，再於2012年省選在該選區連任<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/albertavotes2008/riding/041 |title=CBC.ca Alberta 2008 election results |publisher=CBC |accessdate=May 4, 2012 |archive-date=2015-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101193508/http://www.cbc.ca/albertavotes2008/riding/041 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

美臣於2014年4月辭任新民主黨黨魁後，諾特利宣佈角逐該職位，並於同年10月18日舉行的黨魁選舉中在首輪投票以70%得票率當選<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/rachel-notley-is-the-new-leader-of-the-alberta-ndp-1.2804396 |title=Rachel Notley is the new leader of the Alberta NDP |date=2014-10-18 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2016-10-20 |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223054316/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/rachel-notley-is-the-new-leader-of-the-alberta-ndp-1.2804396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了領導新民主黨黨團外，諾特利亦在省議會内擔任該黨的衛生、國際和各級政府關係、婦女地位和法律事務評議員<ref>{{cite web|title=NDP Leader Rachel Notley releases critic, committee assignments|url=http://albertandp.ca/news/details/ndp_leader_rachel_notley_releases_critic_committee_assignments|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20141115184242/http://albertandp.ca/news/details/ndp_leader_rachel_notley_releases_critic_committee_assignments|archivedate=2014-11-15}}</ref>。

===2015年省選===
[[File:Rachel-Notley-Sworn-In-2015.jpg|thumb]]]]

國際油價從2014年末起下滑，重創以能源業為重心的亞省經濟，省府庫房收入亦驟減。進步保守黨政府於2015年3月公佈財政預算案，錄得亞省歷來最高的50億元赤字，省府遂增加多項服務收費<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-03-28/headline1427523728d5504219.html | title=省服務全面加費 彭迪思籲共度時艱 不敷之數高達70億 | author=郭康立 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-03-28 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020103840/http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-03-28/headline1427523728d5504219.html | archive-date=2016-10-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。為了獲取選民授權省府整頓財務，[[亞伯達省省長|省長]][[彭迪思|彭迪思]]於2015年4月7日請示亞省省督解散省議會，並於同年5月5日舉行省選<ref name="GM150407">{{cite web|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-to-hold-election-on-may-5/article23821249/|title=Jim Prentice seeks mandate on May 5 in cautious Alberta election bid|first=Justin|last=Giovannetti|work=《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》|date=2015-04-07|accessdate=2016-10-19|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019060637/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-to-hold-election-on-may-5/article23821249/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-04-08/province1428488107d5521806.html | title=提早1年 亞省突宣布5月5日省選 | author=劉培慶 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-04-08 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305004845/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-04-08/province1428488107d5521806.html | archive-date=2017-03-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。一批原本隸屬[[官方反對黨|官方反對黨]]野玫瑰黨（{{lang|en|Wildrose Party}}）的省議員轉投進步保守黨，大傷野玫瑰黨元氣，外界評論因此普遍認為進步保守黨極有可能繼續執政<ref name="GM150407"/>，而在愛民頓一帶有相當支持的新民主黨則被認為有機成為官方反對黨<ref>{{cite web|url=http://metronews.ca/news/edmonton/1363359/alberta-ndp-insiders-says-path-rachel-notleys-history-victory-started-long-before-election-began/|title=Alberta NDP insiders say path to Rachel Notley's historic victory started long before election began|first=Ryan|last=Tumilty|date=7 May 2015|accessdate=17 May 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150511004539/http://metronews.ca/news/edmonton/1363359/alberta-ndp-insiders-says-path-rachel-notleys-history-victory-started-long-before-election-began/|archive-date=2015-05-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/canadian-politics/as-pc-and-wildrose-struggle-alberta-ndp-has-real-shot-at-becoming-official-opposition|title=As PCs and Wildrose struggle, Alberta NDP has a real shot at becoming official opposition|first=Jen|last=Gerson|date=2 April 2015|accessdate=15 May 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/alberta-election-2015-the-real-race-is-for-2nd-place-1.3024277|title=Alberta election 2015: The real race is for 2nd place|first=Rob|last=Brown|date=7 April 2015|accessdate=22 June 2015|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225221700/https://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/alberta-election-2015-the-real-race-is-for-2nd-place-1.3024277|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

隨著省選日期將至，民調顯示三大政黨的支持度不相伯仲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/alberta-election-more-horse-race-than-coronation-with-two-weeks-left-1.3039681|title=Alberta election more horse race than coronation with two weeks left|first=Dean|last=Bennett|date=19 April 2015|accessdate=15 May 2015|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225092716/https://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/alberta-election-more-horse-race-than-coronation-with-two-weeks-left-1.3039681|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有見部分省民不滿進步保守黨發表的財政預算案，諾特利表示新民主黨若執政的話將提高企業稅和取消增加省府服務收費<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-ndps-notley-is-preaching-transformation-and-finding-hope/article24120272/|title=Alberta NDP's Notley is preaching transformation and finding hope|first=Justin|last=Giovannetti|date=24 April 2015|accessdate=15 May 2015|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308163533/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-ndps-notley-is-preaching-transformation-and-finding-hope/article24120272/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。諾特利在這次省選的唯一一場電視辯論中，被視為是眾黨魁中表現最佳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/alberta-leaders-debate-poll-suggests-ndp-s-rachel-notley-won-1.3047233|title=Alberta leaders debate: Poll suggests NDP's Rachel Notley won|first=Rick|last=McConnell|date=24 April 2015|accessdate=15 May 2015|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301075033/https://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/alberta-leaders-debate-poll-suggests-ndp-s-rachel-notley-won-1.3047233|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

省選前一星期，新民主黨的支持度抛離其他政黨，而該黨最終在省選贏取省議會87個議席中的54席，以多數姿態首次上台執政之餘，亦同時結束進步保守黨在亞省連續執政44年的歲月<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-05-06/headline1430907708d5565762.html | title=亞省變天 NDP上台 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-05-06 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305004838/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-05-06/headline1430907708d5565762.html | archive-date=2017-03-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。諾特利在自己的選區連任省議員，並於2015年5月24日宣誓成為第17任[[亞伯達省省長|亞伯達省省長]]<ref>"[http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/rachel-notley-sworn-in-as-alberta-premier-reveals-cabinet-1.3085645 Rachel Notley sworn in as Alberta premier, reveals cabinet] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/rachel-notley-sworn-in-as-alberta-premier-reveals-cabinet-1.3085645 |date=20161231033213 }}," ''CBC News'' May 24, 2015.</ref>。她委任的内閣成員只有12人，僅佔省議會全體議員總數的14%，為全國眾省中規模最小<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.edmontonjournal.com/2015/05/21/just-how-small-is-rachel-notleys-cabinet-proportionally-its-pretty-darn-small/|title=Just how small is Rachel Notley's cabinet? Proportionally, it's pretty darn small|date=May 21, 2015|first=Stuart|last=Thomson|publisher=《愛民頓日報》|accessdate=May 22, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522050247/http://blogs.edmontonjournal.com/2015/05/21/just-how-small-is-rachel-notleys-cabinet-proportionally-its-pretty-darn-small/|archive-date=2015-05-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

===省長生涯===
諾特利於2015年11月22日公布更新後的亞省應對氣候變化策略，當中包括從2017年起實施碳税、引入油砂業排放上限、逐步減少以燃煤發電（目標為2030年全面終結）、計劃在十年來將甲烷排放量減半、以及引入措施鼓勵再生能源<ref>{{cite web |url=http://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/themes/5538f80701925b5033000001/attachments/original/1431112969/Alberta_NDP_Platform_2015.pdf?1431112969 |title=Election Platform 2015 |format=pdf |website=Alberta NDP |accessdate=December 22, 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304185556/http://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/themes/5538f80701925b5033000001/attachments/original/1431112969/Alberta_NDP_Platform_2015.pdf?1431112969 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Roberts |first=David |date=November 25, 2015 |title=Alberta's new carbon tax isn't revenue neutral. That's the best thing about it. |url=https://www.vox.com/2015/11/25/9801614/alberta-carbon-tax-revenue-neutral |website=Vox |access-date=December 23, 2016 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308185525/https://www.vox.com/2015/11/25/9801614/alberta-carbon-tax-revenue-neutral |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="abcarbonplan">{{cite news|last1=Giovannetti|first1=Justin|last2=Jones|first2=Jeffrey|title=Alberta carbon plan a major pivot in environmental policy|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-to-release-climate-change-policy-at-edmonton-science-centre/article27433002/|accessdate=7 May 2016|work=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|date=22 November 2015|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220143540/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-to-release-climate-change-policy-at-edmonton-science-centre/article27433002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此外，諾特利任職省長期間，新民主黨政府凍結專上學生學費<ref>{{cite news |last=Mertz |first=Emily |date=September 8, 2015 |title=Alberta NDP government begins tuition freeze for post-secondary students |url=http://globalnews.ca/news/2208840/alberta-ndp-government-begins-tuition-freeze-for-post-secondary-students/ |website=Global News |access-date=November 26, 2016 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301000202/http://globalnews.ca/news/2208840/alberta-ndp-government-begins-tuition-freeze-for-post-secondary-students/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而省内最低工資則從2015年的每小時$10.20逐步增加至2018年的每小時$15.00<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bennett|first1=Dean|title=It's official: Alberta's minimum wage will be $15 an hour by 2018|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/2936591/its-official-albertas-minimum-wage-will-be-15-an-hour-by-2018/|accessdate=2019-05-04|work=Canadian Press, via Global News|date=2016-09-13|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116064955/https://globalnews.ca/news/2936591/its-official-albertas-minimum-wage-will-be-15-an-hour-by-2018/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2019年省選===
進步保守黨和野玫瑰黨於2017年合併成[[聯合保守黨|聯合保守黨]]，亞省右派票源得以團結，此後聯合保守黨在多項民調的支持度皆大幅拋離新民主黨。在2019年4月舉行的省選中，聯合保守黨輕易贏取省議會多數議席上台執政，新民主黨則贏取省議會87席中的24席成為第二大黨（即[[官方反對黨|官方反對黨]]）<ref>{{cite news|title=康尼宣誓任亞省省長 暫不斷卑詩油氣供應|url=https://www.singtao.ca/3416428/2019-05-01/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E4%BB%BB%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E7%9C%81%E9%95%B7-%E6%9A%AB%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E5%8D%91%E8%A9%A9%E6%B2%B9%E6%B0%A3%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89/?variant=zh-hk|accessdate=2019-05-04|newspaper=《星島日報》|date=2019-05-01|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504223145/https://www.singtao.ca/3416428/2019-05-01/post-%e5%ba%b7%e5%b0%bc%e5%ae%a3%e8%aa%93%e4%bb%bb%e4%ba%9e%e7%9c%81%e7%9c%81%e9%95%b7-%e6%9a%ab%e4%b8%8d%e6%96%b7%e5%8d%91%e8%a9%a9%e6%b2%b9%e6%b0%a3%e4%be%9b%e6%87%89/?variant=zh-hk|dead-url=no}}</ref>。諾特利保着自己選區議席，表示會留任新民主黨黨魁<ref>{{cite news|title=保守黨贏亞省省選 康尼組大多數政府|url=https://m.singtao.ca/toronto_hk_st/52/3381242-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E8%B4%8F%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E7%B5%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C/|accessdate=2019-05-04|newspaper=《星島日報》|author=張文慈|date=2019-04-17|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504223125/https://m.singtao.ca/toronto_hk_st/52/3381242-%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%88%e9%bb%a8%e8%b4%8f%e4%ba%9e%e7%9c%81%e7%9c%81%e9%81%b8-%e5%ba%b7%e5%b0%bc%e7%b5%84%e5%a4%a7%e5%a4%9a%e6%95%b8%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並從新一屆省議會會期起出任亞伯達官方反對黨主席。

